<h3>
	Support
</h3>

<p>
	If you have found a bug or would like to request a feature with nsm then do so through one of the official nsm repositories on <a href="https://bitbucket.org/nifty-site-manager/nsm/src/master/">BitBucket</a>, <a href="https://github.com/nifty-site-manager/nsm">GitHub</a> or <a href="https://gitlab.com/nifty-site-manager/nsm">GitLab</a>.
</p>

<p>
	If you have found a typo or would like to suggest a change to the nsm site then do so through one of the nsm site repositories on <a href="https://bitbucket.org/nifty-site-manager/nifty-site-manager.bitbucket.io/src/master/">BitBucket</a>, <a href="https://github.com/nifty-site-manager/nifty-site-manager.github.io">GitHub</a> or <a href="https://gitlab.com/nifty-site-manager/nifty-site-manager.gitlab.io">GitLab</a>.
</p>

